body.name: AWQM Dining Room Table Set, Kitchen Set with 2 Benches, Ideal for Home, and Room, Breakfast of 43.3x23.6x28.5 inches, Benches 38.5x11.8x17.5 Black
features: High Quality: The Dining Table Set is Constructed with MDF wood board and metal square tube in rich grain finish for greater stability and sturdiness.

Modern Design & Breakfast/Dinner with Whole Family: 3 Piece dining table and chairs set comes complete with a spacious table(43.3 x 23.6 x 28.5 inches) and 2 benches(38.5 * 11.8 * 17.5 inches each), modern and stylish design make this 3 piece dining room set easily blend into anywhere you want in your house and also for small spaces.

Space-saving Design: Both benches can be conveniently tucked under the table, making these benches space-saving and convenient when not in use. And help conveniently preparing and delivering cuisine dishes to the kitchen table top avoid unexpected tripping.
Easy to clean: Dining table set for 4 has a metal frame with wood table top and seats are rugged and water-resistant, and easy to wipe clean with damp cloth when there are spills or messes.

Multi-functional & Easy Assembly: Perfectly used as a dining table, computer table, study desk, writing desk or soho working table, industrial DIY workshop table and benches set. Easy assembly with detailed installation manual and organized packaging.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Waterproof & Easy Clean MDF texture finish on surface of table and 2 benches provides excellent waterproof and dust proof performance and against unexpected scratching to keep great appearance for a long time. Longevity & Stability The robust structure of the 3 pieces dining table provides extra stability for family having breakfast, lunch or dinner together, and being more durable against weight capacity up to 250 lbs. Thickened Pipe Steel pipe material with durable coating finish to protect the steel frame and legs of table and benches from being aged by natural elements, and provide longer service life.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very Functional and Minimalist!
reviews.reviewText: The AWQM Industrial Brown 43" Bar Table Set is a stylish and functional addition to any space. Its industrial design, featuring a 43-inch bar table and accompanying stools for four, adds a modern touch to any environment. The rich brown finish not only complements a variety of decor styles but also exudes a warm and inviting ambiance. The sturdy construction of both the table and stools ensures durability, making it suitable for both residential and commercial use. The thoughtful design provides ample space for socializing or dining, making it an ideal choice for gatherings with friends and family. The AWQM Industrial Brown Bar Table Set effortlessly blends contemporary aesthetics with practical functionality, creating a chic and welcoming setting for socializing and dining.
